@startuml
title LaunchPad Home Aggregation Sequence

actor Student as User
participant "Client App" as Client
participant "LaunchPadHomeController" as HomeController
participant "LaunchPadAggregator\n(Facade)" as Aggregator
participant "SandboxService" as Sandbox
participant "SideHustleService" as SideHustle
database "LaunchPad Data Store" as DB

User -> Client: Visit LaunchPad home
Client -> HomeController: GET /launchpad/home/{userId}\nAuthorization: Bearer <jwt>
note right of HomeController
	JWT is validated before controller handling.
end note
HomeController -> Aggregator: getHomeView(userId)

Aggregator -> Sandbox: listByStudent(userId)
Sandbox -> DB: query sandboxes by student_id
DB --> Sandbox: sandbox rows
Sandbox --> Aggregator: sandbox summaries

Aggregator -> SideHustle: listByStudent(userId)
SideHustle -> DB: query side_hustles by student_id
DB --> SideHustle: side_hustle rows
SideHustle --> Aggregator: side_hustle summaries\n(with hasOpenPositions)

Aggregator -> Aggregator: compose LaunchPadHomeView\ninTheLabCount = sandboxes.size()\nliveVenturesCount = count(status=LIVE_VENTURE)
Aggregator --> HomeController: LaunchPadHomeView
HomeController --> Client: 200 OK + aggregated home JSON
Client --> User: Display LaunchPad overview

@enduml